{
  "stem": "4693.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So she went to other orthopedic surgeons, because she didn't trust that it is possible.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So everyone of them said that if Professor Gauck wants to do it, to let him do it, because he is the top guy.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And actually he operated on me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I was for many months in the clinic-- in his clinic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And before the operations my only question was would I be able to play soccer-- or football, as we called it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So when I woke up after the operation, the first thing I ask him if I was promised a football, a-- a ball.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And the ball was next to my bed as I still remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "It took a while to, but I started walking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And it never gave me any difficulties later in my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And I was in the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I was doing sports.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I am a pretty skier.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I am still skiing, snow skiing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And I want to say, because it made a difference, influenced quite a bit of my life later.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Anyway, coming back to my family, as mentioned, I was going to school, attending a private school-- non-Jewish School.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "There were some Jews, who was constituted more or less maybe 20% or below of the population.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Considering that the cities of Poland, or towns of Poland, had a very high percentage of Jews, this was very little.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And I was going to school in Bedzen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "This was a place from which my mother came, or her family was living.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And Bedzen was another-- it was a Jewish school, one of two only, as far as I know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Schools well teaching Hebrew in Poland, the other one was in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, only 7 kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was connected by tram and by train.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
